<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_83" id="40v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_83_r1l5">Dem <expan>erwırdıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geıſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Bruder Jobſen <expan>p<ex>ro</ex>uincıal</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l6"><expan>Miniſt<ex>er</ex></expan> Barfuſſen Ordens in <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Deẅtſchen landen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_83_r1l7"><expan>Erwırdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als vor <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> von gabe vnd <expan>einſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l8">des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> geıſtes mit <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd hılffe . des <expan>erwırdıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Bruder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l9"><expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> levwen <expan>ler<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>göttlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> künſt vnd dıe ʒeıt <expan>Miniſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>barfuſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ordens <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l10"><expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vorfarn in dem <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>geıſtlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> frawen ſand Claren Ordens bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l11">vns ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> / ein <expan>löblıch<ex>er</ex></expan> anfank einr <expan>göttlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> eynikeıt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l12">gemein Jrs leıbs vnd guts <expan>mıteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuhalte<ex>n</ex></expan> . gemacht ward / Des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l13"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> eẅr vorfar . dem got gnedıg ſey fleıſſıg gemüet was daʒ er <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l14">frawen von dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſtul ʒu Rome etlıch brief vnd gnade darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l15">erlangt vnd Jn darcʒuſelbs etlıch <expan>ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd ſtatut ſecʒet vnd macht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l16">mit ſeins ambts Jnſıgel . Vnd vns befalh ſie alſo dabey ʒu hanthaben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l17">Da mıt der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> löblıch anfank ʒu <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> guten mıttel kam / daʒ dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l18">frawen des <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd <expan>Conue<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> . alle <expan>gemeinkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd wıllıklıch ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l19">lobten dıe <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> eynikeıt vnd gemein Jrs leıbs vnd guts vnd auch die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l20"><expan>vorgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> Jrs <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd ſtatut ʒu halten / Daſſelb Jn auch von irem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l21"><expan>Oberſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gen<ex>er</ex>al</expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> ward / Vnd vns eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l22">dem als Jr ʒu <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wart . <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchraıb</expan> / daʒ Jr an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l23"><expan>ſölıche<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan> leben vnd <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geıſtlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Ordnuge<ex>n</ex></expan> ein <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l24">hettet vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> fleıſſ vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>mugen</expan> darcʒu keren wöltet / daʒ es in dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l25"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex></expan> dabey <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd fürbas <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſölt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> etc / als auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l26">das etwıeuıl ʒeıt vnd Jare <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> / löblıch vnd <expan>ordenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l27">Das alles <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erwırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ <expan>wıſſenlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt / Alſo tun wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l28"><expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Daʒ wır mıt <expan>groſſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>miſſfall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l29"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wıe dıe <expan>frawe<ex>n</ex></expan> des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> an <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>löblıch<ex>er</ex></expan> eynikeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l30">vnd gemein <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>obgeſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Öb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> göttlıche gebott vnd auch </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_84" id="41r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l1"> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> Jrſelbs regeln vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſtatut </del> gelüb etwas <expan>weyg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd der vılleıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l2"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>abw<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / Dabey wır <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd <expan>Conue<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> merklıch ſcheden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l3"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> . wo das niht <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex></expan> wurd / Vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l4">mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ . daʒ Jr voran got ʒu lob vnd darnach durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l5"><expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dauor ſein vnd <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> fleıſſ vnd ernſt <expan>onu<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> darcʒu <expan>wende<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l6">vnd keren wellet / als vns dunkt / daʒ Jr von gots vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> ambts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l7">wol ſchuldıg ſeyt / Da mıt ſölıch göttlıch vnd löblıch gemein <expan>Ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l8">vnd ſtatut nıht abgeen . <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gebeſſ<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd veſt <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . als wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l9">vns des vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> guten ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l10">wan Jr wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / daʒ dıe <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> frawen vnd <expan>Conue<ex>n</ex>t</expan> in <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
